DOES SHE HAVE OTHER FAMILY
YOU SHOULD TALK TO?

11:09.030 --> 11:11.328
YEAH. UM...
I'LL TRY CALLING THEM AGAIN.

11:11.370 --> 11:15.238
BUT, DOCTOR, WHAT DO YOU THINK
WE SHOULD DO?

11:15.270 --> 11:17.864
I THINK I SHOULD OPERATE.
AND SOON.

11:20.110 --> 11:22.874
(cell phone case Velcro rips,
buttons click)

11:26.820 --> 11:28.708
(refrigerator door opens)

11:28.750 --> 11:29.910
CELERY.

11:29.950 --> 11:32.214
(radio chatter)

11:32.250 --> 11:36.414
