BRING HIM BACK.

11:53.310 --> 11:55.778
(sniffles and exhales)

11:55.810 --> 11:59.041
OH, GOD. OKAY.

11:59.080 --> 12:01.469
UM, WHAT CAN I DO?

12:01.520 --> 12:04.387
NOTHING. JUST SIT TIGHT.

12:04.420 --> 12:07.787
