12:45.330 --> 12:48.151
(sighs) WHAT?

12:48.200 --> 12:50.361
HE'S OUT THERE SOMEWHERE.

12:50.400 --> 12:52.220
AND WE CAN'T EVEN LEAVE
THE STATION.

12:52.270 --> 12:54.033
OKAY. WE DON'T NEED
TO LEAVE, ALL RIGHT?

12:54.070 --> 12:55.560
WE NEED TO USE OUR HEADS.

12:55.600 --> 12:58.307
ANDY, WE WORK TOGETHER,
WE WILL FIND HIM

12:58.340 --> 12:59.466
'CAUSE THAT'S WHAT WE DO.

13:02.480 --> 13:06.007
