ANOTHER WORKSPACE?

13:09.950 --> 13:12.009
(exhales deeply)

13:12.050 --> 13:14.484
HE'S YOUR LITTLE BROTHER.
YOU KNOW HIM BETTER THAN ANYONE.

13:14.520 --> 13:18.058
PLEASE.
LOOK, I-I-I KNEW
HE WAS SPINNING OUT.

13:18.090 --> 13:19.455
