(voice breaking) OF--OF

13:33.480 --> 13:36.131
ABDUCTING CHILDREN--OF--
OF HURTING CHILDREN.

13:36.180 --> 13:37.442
OF COURSE HE'S UPSET.

13:37.480 --> 13:39.448
UPSET?

13:39.480 --> 13:41.573
ABE, YOUR BROTHER'S
SHOOTING POLICE OFFICERS.

13:41.620 --> 13:45.545
I DON'T KNOW WHERE HE IS.
I SWEAR TO GOD, I DON'T KNOW.

13:45.590 --> 13:47.217
I DON'T EVEN WANT
TO SEE HIM AGAIN.

