14:09.980 --> 14:13.416
(pants and wheezes)

14:13.450 --> 14:17.079
(handcuffs click)

14:17.120 --> 14:18.439
(breathy voice) KEVIN...
(exhales)

14:18.490 --> 14:20.082
(normal voice)
KEVIN, RIGHT?

14:20.120 --> 14:22.156
(clacks)

