(blows air) YOU KNOW.

14:35.470 --> 14:38.268
(exhales sharply, sniffs)
IT'S GONNA BE GOOD.

14:38.310 --> 14:41.029
OKAY. KEVIN,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

