14:50.350 --> 14:52.318
I ARRESTED THE GUY
THAT ASSAULTED YOU.

14:52.350 --> 14:54.318
I WAS IN YOUR HOUSE.
I CALLED E.M.S. FOR YOU.

14:54.360 --> 14:57.284
FUNNY, CONSIDERING
YOU PUT HIM UP TO IT.
WHAT?

14:57.330 --> 14:59.218
YEAH, I KNOW
WHAT'S GOING ON.

14:59.260 --> 15:01.296
LOOK, I SAW WHAT SHE DID.
(door squeaks)

15:01.330 --> 15:03.525
