15:58.120 --> 15:59.109
(grunts)

16:02.120 --> 16:04.020
GAIL, WE'RE GONNA FIND HIM.
THAT'S WHAT PEOPLE

16:04.060 --> 16:06.085
KEPT SAYING TO ME
WHEN CHRISTIAN WAS MISSING.

16:06.130 --> 16:07.495
I KNOW THEY WERE JUST TRYING
TO MAKE ME FEEL BETTER,

16:07.530 --> 16:10.465
BUT IT WORKED. SO, GAIL, WE'RE--
WE'RE GONNA FIND HIM.

16:10.500 --> 16:12.491
THAT'S ALL I WANT.

16:12.530 --> 16:15.067
OKAY, WE FIND OLIVER.

16:15.100 --> 16:17.534
HE MAKES A VERY DUMB JOKE.

16:17.570 --> 16:21.131
CHLOE GETS OUT OF THE HOSPITAL.
