17:12.230 --> 17:13.822
HIS ALIBI--
IT JUST DIDN'T ADD UP.

17:13.860 --> 17:16.397
THEY NEVER FOUND THE BOY--
MARLO. MARLO, RIGHT NOW
WE JUST NEED TO FIND FORD, OKAY?

17:16.430 --> 17:19.627
Y--I KNOW. I--
LOOK, YOU'VE BEEN TRACKING
THIS GUY FOR WEEKS.

17:19.670 --> 17:21.558
LET'S JUST--LET'S JUST
TALK IT THROUGH,

17:21.600 --> 17:23.238
SEE IF WE CAN
FIGURE THIS OUT, OKAY?
ALL RIGHT.

17:23.270 --> 17:26.808
OKAY, UH, THE 11th?
I MEAN, WORK. WORK.

17:26.840 --> 17:28.273
THERE WAS A DROP-OFF
AT THE STORE,

17:28.310 --> 17:29.834
