18:34.780 --> 18:35.872
(computer beeps)

18:35.910 --> 18:37.775
SAM, THEY'RE ALL
FROM THIS WEEK.

18:37.810 --> 18:39.846
(door buzzes and beeps)
ABE...

18:39.880 --> 18:42.872
QUEEN AND SHANNON--
MEAN ANYTHING TO YOU?
