41:11.870 --> 41:12.791
THANK YOU.

41:12.830 --> 41:15.537
HEY, DOC, DOC, CAN WE GO IN?
CAN WE SEE HIM?

41:15.570 --> 41:16.798
NOT YET. I'M SORRY.

41:16.840 --> 41:18.034
DOC.

41:18.070 --> 41:19.606
PLEASE?

41:21.110 --> 41:22.771
